  "original_title": "\u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dc0 \u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Chinese friend leaves",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Chinese exploration ship Yuan Wang 5 (22), which was anchored at Hambantota Port, left Hambantota International Port in the afternoon.",
        "So far, there has been no news regarding what work this expedition ship did when it arrived at Hambantota International Port 16 days ago.",
        "When the officer in charge of the media section was asked to request the Hambantota port authorities to even report the occasion of the ship's departure from the Hambantota port to the media, there was no attempt to give permission for that."
      ],
